WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:03.070
Good morning, family! How are y'all

00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:05.829
doing? I just wanted to

00:00:05.839 --> 00:00:08.509
say thank you all for all the

00:00:08.519 --> 00:00:10.870
kindness. We're at this prayer

00:00:10.880 --> 00:00:11.990
conference right now, still in

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.829
our hotel. We've been

00:00:13.829 --> 00:00:13.839
here

00:00:13.839 --> 00:00:16.230
for two days, and many

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:18.349
of you traveled to

00:00:18.359 --> 00:00:20.910
see Sister

00:00:20.910 --> 00:00:20.920
Billye

00:00:20.920 --> 00:00:23.509
and support her ministry.

00:00:23.509 --> 00:00:23.519
We

00:00:23.519 --> 00:00:25.589
want to say thank you to all the

00:00:25.599 --> 00:00:27.710
subscribers who said they came here

00:00:27.720 --> 00:00:30.669
because of what we said to

00:00:30.679 --> 00:00:32.990
support Sister

00:00:32.990 --> 00:00:33.000
Billye.

00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:35.030
The prayer conference

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:36.430
has been amazing and such a

00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:39.310
blessing. I want to say to

00:00:39.320 --> 00:00:42.270
all of you who traveled so

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:43.670
far—from

00:00:43.680 --> 00:00:45.549
Chicago, New

00:00:45.559 --> 00:00:47.389
York, Los

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:49.790
Angeles,

00:00:49.790 --> 00:00:49.800
and

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:51.709
all over the United States—to

00:00:51.709 --> 00:00:51.719
support

00:00:51.719 --> 00:00:53.630
this conference

00:00:53.630 --> 00:00:53.640
and

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:56.430
pray for our nation:

00:00:56.440 --> 00:00:59.349
God bless you all. I

00:00:59.349 --> 00:00:59.359
know

00:00:59.359 --> 00:01:01.869
it took a lot of time,

00:01:01.879 --> 00:01:04.869
effort, resources, and money

00:01:04.869 --> 00:01:04.879
for

00:01:04.879 --> 00:01:07.870
hotels and food. I know some of

00:01:07.870 --> 00:01:07.880
you

00:01:07.880 --> 00:01:10.390
spent thousands to do this,

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:13.749
and I know God is an abundant

00:01:13.759 --> 00:01:16.030
supplier who will reward you for

00:01:16.030 --> 00:01:16.040
helping

00:01:16.040 --> 00:01:17.910
pray for our nation. Thank

00:01:17.920 --> 00:01:20.590
you for supporting Sister

00:01:20.590 --> 00:01:20.600
Billye

00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:22.310
and the family. They

00:01:22.310 --> 00:01:22.320
are

00:01:22.320 --> 00:01:24.870
some of the nicest people I have

00:01:24.870 --> 00:01:24.880
ever

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:26.910
met.

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:30.390
Seriously, y'all, they are genuinely nice

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:32.749
people. Sometimes you get around

00:01:32.759 --> 00:01:34.910
Christians in upper leadership

00:01:34.920 --> 00:01:36.389
and you think they might be stuck

00:01:36.399 --> 00:01:39.190
up, but these

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:42.670
people are really good people.

00:01:42.680 --> 00:01:44.389
I've been really impressed with how

00:01:44.399 --> 00:01:47.270
kind they've been to us. I'm

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:49.469
grateful

00:01:49.469 --> 00:01:49.479
for

00:01:49.479 --> 00:01:51.350
their love toward my family.

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.630
She

00:01:53.640 --> 00:01:55.630
let me talk last night

00:01:55.640 --> 00:01:57.429
about the prophetic words the Lord is

00:01:57.439 --> 00:02:00.749
showing me, and we prayed against

00:02:00.759 --> 00:02:02.709
some of the things the Lord

00:02:02.709 --> 00:02:02.719
showed

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:04.990
me. It

00:02:04.990 --> 00:02:05.000
is

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:09.630
amazing to see

00:02:09.640 --> 00:02:12.150
what the Lord has done in this

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:14.309
amount of time. I felt

00:02:14.319 --> 00:02:17.670
like we were one of those big

00:02:17.670 --> 00:02:17.680
mega-ships

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:20.470
plowing through the ice in the spirit

00:02:20.480 --> 00:02:22.550
realm concerning President Trump and the

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:24.630
election. I could

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:26.910
feel the shifting in the spirit as we were

00:02:26.920 --> 00:02:29.390
praying and interceding.

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:33.190
It felt like

00:02:33.200 --> 00:02:35.229
we were plowing through demonic

00:02:35.239 --> 00:02:38.270
strongholds with so many seasoned prayer warriors. There

00:02:38.270 --> 00:02:38.280
are

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:40.630
a lot

00:02:40.630 --> 00:02:40.640
of

00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:43.589
people

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:49.550
standing for this nation.

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:51.630
I

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:53.630
believe beyond a shadow of

00:02:53.630 --> 00:02:53.640
a

00:02:53.640 --> 00:02:56.910
doubt that Trump is going to win

00:02:56.920 --> 00:02:59.149
this election and we're going to see

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:01.550
victory.

00:03:01.550 --> 00:03:01.560
As

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:03.710
Sister Lynn said

00:03:03.720 --> 00:03:06.750
today,

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:10.149
'Do not become

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:13.149
complacent after you see the

00:03:13.149 --> 00:03:13.159
victory.'We

00:03:13.159 --> 00:03:16.070
have got to keep our foot on the gas

00:03:16.070 --> 00:03:16.080
and

00:03:16.080 --> 00:03:18.270
keep on

00:03:18.280 --> 00:03:20.509
praying over the cabinet and his decisions

00:03:20.509 --> 00:03:20.519
on

00:03:20.519 --> 00:03:23.789
who he surrounds himself with. We pray that he

00:03:23.799 --> 00:03:27.830
puts Godly men and women in positions

00:03:27.830 --> 00:03:27.840
of

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:30.630
counsel so that when he wins,

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:36.350
it will be by a landslide. We

00:03:36.350 --> 00:03:36.360
are also

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:38.429
believing

00:03:38.429 --> 00:03:38.439
that

00:03:38.439 --> 00:03:39.869
God will take the

00:03:39.879 --> 00:03:43.190
House and the Senate

00:03:43.190 --> 00:03:43.200
for

00:03:43.200 --> 00:03:48.110
a supernatural move.

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:50.470
The next four years should be

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:53.869
smooth so that we can have

00:03:53.879 --> 00:03:57.589
a revival.

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:59.550
We prayed about the financial collapse

00:03:59.560 --> 00:04:01.069
and the things the Lord

00:04:01.079 --> 00:04:03.670
showed me. I

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:05.630
still feel something in the natural, but

00:04:05.630 --> 00:04:05.640
I

00:04:05.640 --> 00:04:07.429
am not moved by what I see or

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:09.710
feel.

00:04:09.720 --> 00:04:12.470
I still have a caution and

00:04:14.760 --> 00:04:17.550
feel we have prayer to do

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:20.349
concerning the

00:04:20.359 --> 00:04:24.510
economy.

00:04:24.520 --> 00:04:26.710
When

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:28.749
I gave the word about

00:04:28.759 --> 00:04:30.670
the economy, the Lord rebuked

00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:32.870
me and said, 'Brandon, you need to tell

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:35.510
My people do not

00:04:35.510 --> 00:04:35.520
fear.'He

00:04:35.520 --> 00:04:39.510
said,

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:42.270
'I will supply all your needs according

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:44.150
to My riches

00:04:44.150 --> 00:04:44.160
in

00:04:44.160 --> 00:04:47.070
glory by Christ Jesus.'This is not for the believer; He said

00:04:50.360 --> 00:04:53.029
He

00:04:56.120 --> 00:04:58.590
will provide for His beloved. If

00:04:58.600 --> 00:05:00.830
you're a tither and a giver and

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:03.350
believe that Jesus is your Jehovah

00:05:03.360 --> 00:05:05.990
Jireh,

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:08.230
He will provide for you

00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:10.990
regardless of whether the bottom falls out

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.909
tomorrow. I was looking at

00:05:12.919 --> 00:05:15.870
statistics today, and

00:05:15.870 --> 00:05:15.880
a

00:05:15.880 --> 00:05:18.189
news article

00:05:18.189 --> 00:05:18.199
stated

00:05:18.199 --> 00:05:19.950
that in the last three

00:05:19.960 --> 00:05:22.270
weeks, we've spent half a trillion

00:05:22.280 --> 00:05:24.350
dollars more in the deficit.

00:05:24.360 --> 00:05:27.270
It was

00:05:27.280 --> 00:05:30.150
skyrocketing on the graph.

00:05:31.479 --> 00:05:34.430
Our national debt is $35

00:05:34.440 --> 00:05:36.990
trillion now. Are we moved by fear? No,

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:40.230
but we know the

00:05:40.240 --> 00:05:42.550
signs of the times.

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:44.870
The dollar is

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:48.029
in the way; they have to take it down

00:05:48.039 --> 00:05:50.189
to bring in the

00:05:50.189 --> 00:05:50.199
one-world

00:05:50.199 --> 00:05:54.909
government and the digital

00:05:54.919 --> 00:05:57.870
platform.

00:06:00.120 --> 00:06:03.230
We can lessen the

00:06:03.240 --> 00:06:05.189
effect so that it will not

00:06:05.199 --> 00:06:08.270
affect you.

00:06:10.160 --> 00:06:12.510
I want you to be

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:15.150
prepared spiritually, interceding for

00:06:15.160 --> 00:06:17.150
your house

00:06:17.160 --> 00:06:19.870
and listening to Him on how to

00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:23.830
intercede for our nation.

00:06:25.800 --> 00:06:28.589
We don't get into fear; we walk in

00:06:28.599 --> 00:06:32.150
faith.

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:33.710
That's why I brought up

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:35.909
food supplies and

00:06:35.919 --> 00:06:38.350
the dollar

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:40.390
crash.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:55.150
I heard a

00:06:55.160 --> 00:06:56.710
testimony

00:06:56.710 --> 00:06:56.720
about

00:06:56.720 --> 00:06:59.950
people during the Great Depression

00:06:59.950 --> 00:06:59.960
who

00:06:59.960 --> 00:07:02.189
were consistent

00:07:02.199 --> 00:07:05.430
tithers

00:07:05.440 --> 00:07:07.110
and

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:10.150
never lacked a job or any good

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:12.670
thing.

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:25.710
My granny told me it was terrible;

00:07:25.710 --> 00:07:25.720
she was 106 when

00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:27.790
she died and

00:07:27.790 --> 00:07:27.800
said

00:07:27.800 --> 00:07:30.430
it was terrible

00:07:30.440 --> 00:07:32.029
going through the depression,

00:07:32.039 --> 00:07:34.510
but they weren't tithers

00:07:34.510 --> 00:07:34.520
then.

00:07:34.520 --> 00:07:36.350
However,

00:07:36.360 --> 00:07:38.749
I heard

00:07:38.759 --> 00:07:40.990
of people like Brother

00:07:40.990 --> 00:07:41.000
Kenneth

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:43.150
Hagin

00:07:43.150 --> 00:07:43.160
who

00:07:43.160 --> 00:07:45.029
believed in their covenant and made it through. Regardless

00:07:45.029 --> 00:07:45.039
of what the economy does,

00:07:45.039 --> 00:07:47.350
God

00:07:51.070 --> 00:07:51.080
will

00:07:55.759 --> 00:07:57.710
turn it around for

00:07:57.720 --> 00:08:00.029
your favor.

00:08:05.230 --> 00:08:05.240
We

00:08:11.159 --> 00:08:14.430
are

00:08:19.479 --> 00:08:21.110
overcomers by the blood of the Lamb and

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:22.990
the word of

00:08:22.990 --> 00:08:23.000
our

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:24.670
testimony.

00:08:24.680 --> 00:08:27.189
If I ever come off as a

00:08:27.199 --> 00:08:28.909
fearmonger, I want to emphasize that there is always

00:08:28.919 --> 00:08:30.950
faith

00:08:30.960 --> 00:08:33.149
to believe yourself

00:08:33.159 --> 00:08:36.110
out of any trap the devil

00:08:36.120 --> 00:08:38.430
tries to

00:08:38.440 --> 00:08:41.790
set.

00:08:41.800 --> 00:08:44.750
Whatsoever a man soweth, that

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:47.990
will he also reap.

00:08:54.399 --> 00:08:56.110
This week has been

00:08:58.720 --> 00:09:00.509
interesting. When we went to Billy Burke,

00:09:00.519 --> 00:09:03.829
three major words were given to

00:09:03.839 --> 00:09:05.829
my wife and me. We were praying

00:09:05.839 --> 00:09:08.550
for Megan, and I

00:09:08.560 --> 00:09:10.910
can see a supernatural change already

00:09:10.920 --> 00:09:13.030
taking place in her. She is talking

00:09:13.040 --> 00:09:16.630
more in the last 48 hours than we've

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:19.110
ever heard

00:09:19.110 --> 00:09:19.120
in

00:09:19.120 --> 00:09:22.430
her whole life.

00:09:25.560 --> 00:09:27.389
After the man of God prayed, she

00:09:27.389 --> 00:09:27.399
used

00:09:27.399 --> 00:09:29.990
appropriate words at the

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:33.069
right timing.

00:09:33.079 --> 00:09:35.150
She was even jabbering and chirping

00:09:35.150 --> 00:09:35.160
to

00:09:35.160 --> 00:09:37.910
the people in front of us. I

00:09:37.920 --> 00:09:39.670
think

00:09:41.480 --> 00:09:43.430
they got up and left because she was

00:09:44.829 --> 00:09:44.839
disruptive,

00:09:45.720 --> 00:09:49.150
but Megan was

00:09:49.160 --> 00:09:51.710
trying to

00:09:51.720 --> 00:09:53.470
make sentences.

00:09:55.680 --> 00:09:58.949
You can see

00:09:58.959 --> 00:10:00.790
the wheels turning

00:10:00.800 --> 00:10:03.509
in her eyes.

00:10:03.519 --> 00:10:06.750
There is

00:10:06.760 --> 00:10:09.750
a tangible

00:10:09.760 --> 00:10:11.870
turnaround.

00:10:32.800 --> 00:10:35.629
If you are believing for something,

00:10:37.480 --> 00:10:41.350
get submersed in God's

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:45.430
word and do not go

00:10:45.440 --> 00:10:48.190
dry.

00:10:50.160 --> 00:10:52.269
Give

00:10:52.279 --> 00:10:54.230
God the glory

00:10:54.240 --> 00:10:56.389
over every small thing

00:10:56.399 --> 00:10:58.310
that happens because

00:10:58.320 --> 00:11:01.030
it

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:03.430
builds into a miracle.

00:11:05.839 --> 00:11:08.230
Like when she got

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:10.590
potty

00:11:10.600 --> 00:11:12.230
trained;

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:15.030
the doctors told

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:17.949
us we

00:11:17.949 --> 00:11:17.959
would

00:11:17.959 --> 00:11:20.990
more than likely never see

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:23.030
this child be potty trained.

00:11:23.040 --> 00:11:25.150
Professionals tried to

00:11:25.160 --> 00:11:28.310
help us and it did not work;

00:11:33.200 --> 00:11:35.190
they

00:11:35.200 --> 00:11:37.910
said she

00:11:37.920 --> 00:11:39.190
would

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:40.750
wear

00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:42.310
a

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:43.870
diaper

00:11:43.880 --> 00:11:45.030
the

00:11:45.040 --> 00:11:47.190
rest

00:11:47.200 --> 00:11:49.629
of

00:11:49.639 --> 00:11:51.629
her

00:11:53.279 --> 00:11:55.389
life.

00:11:56.720 --> 00:12:00.550
But God

00:12:02.310 --> 00:12:02.320
is

00:12:05.120 --> 00:12:10.509
rich in mercy.

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:17.870
We

00:12:17.880 --> 00:12:19.509
had a glimmer of hope like

00:12:19.509 --> 00:12:19.519
Noah's

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:22.790
olive leaf.

00:12:33.040 --> 00:12:35.230
When he prayed for her the first

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:37.189
time, we stood by faith, and

00:12:42.360 --> 00:12:45.069
now we have

00:12:45.079 --> 00:12:47.110
our second olive

00:12:50.240 --> 00:12:52.910
leaf.

00:12:56.189 --> 00:12:56.199
We

00:13:02.350 --> 00:13:02.360
are

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:06.189
fully

00:13:07.760 --> 00:13:10.750
persuaded,

00:13:13.519 --> 00:13:15.590
just like Abraham,

00:13:23.440 --> 00:13:25.509
that

00:13:25.519 --> 00:13:27.590
what God has promised He is able also to

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:30.590
perform.

00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:33.030
Even

00:13:33.040 --> 00:13:34.949
if

00:13:34.949 --> 00:13:34.959
it

00:13:34.959 --> 00:13:37.710
seems

00:13:37.720 --> 00:13:39.150
impossible,

00:13:39.160 --> 00:13:41.829
all things are possible to

00:13:41.839 --> 00:13:43.629
him that believes.

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:49.430
We've been putting her in an

00:13:49.430 --> 00:13:49.440
environment of faith at these

00:13:49.440 --> 00:13:52.670
services.

00:13:56.920 --> 00:13:59.230
It's

00:13:59.240 --> 00:14:01.430
been stretching her to sit for

00:14:01.430 --> 00:14:01.440
two

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:04.069
services a day,

00:14:04.079 --> 00:14:06.150
and

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:08.030
she's been saying, 'Daddy, my heiny

00:14:09.639 --> 00:14:11.110
hurts,'but

00:14:13.199 --> 00:14:16.030
it's time for

00:14:16.040 --> 00:14:18.710
her to come out.

00:14:25.199 --> 00:14:26.790
Faith

00:14:26.800 --> 00:14:30.269
without works is dead, so

00:14:30.269 --> 00:14:30.279
we

00:14:32.590 --> 00:14:32.600
are

00:14:32.600 --> 00:14:34.870
putting

00:14:34.880 --> 00:14:37.749
our

00:14:37.749 --> 00:14:37.759
faith

00:14:39.829 --> 00:14:39.839
in

00:14:39.839 --> 00:14:41.189
action.

00:14:41.199 --> 00:14:44.189
Diana refuses to treat her as

00:14:44.189 --> 00:14:44.199
anything

00:14:44.199 --> 00:14:47.509
other than healed.

00:14:47.519 --> 00:14:49.269
We

00:14:49.279 --> 00:14:51.749
are

00:14:51.759 --> 00:14:54.030
resisting

00:14:59.040 --> 00:15:01.150
the

00:15:08.470 --> 00:15:08.480
symptoms.

00:15:16.040 --> 00:15:17.629
We're going to sit down in

00:15:17.639 --> 00:15:18.910
restaurants

00:15:18.920 --> 00:15:21.189
as a family now. For years, we sat in the car

00:15:21.199 --> 00:15:21.910
and

